        <h3>What's New in 2026.03.17</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Streaming: hypothesis instrumentation (debug builds only) — tracks first-hypothesis timing, growth direction, peak text, and hypothesis-vs-confirmed comparison to guide latency improvements</li>
          <li>Streaming: grow-only dry-run simulation (debug builds only) — simulates what a grow-only hypothesis insertion strategy would produce at the cursor, logging word-match accuracy against confirmed text at stop time</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
          All transcription happens 100% locally on your device.
        </p>
      ]]></description>
